content:
Got it — expense-splitting app prototype, 8 screens, MVP for alpha testing. I'll go with a **human/approachable** direction: clean neutral foundations, teal-green accent (fitting for finance), comfortable radii, and crisp hierarchy — more beautiful and less cluttered than Splitwise.

Now I'll create the index launcher and start building screens. Let me write the first batch in parallel:

8 screens built — **SplitFlow**: landing, auth, expenses dashboard, new expense, receipt scanning, invite (QR + email), settle up, and settings. Teal-green accent on clean neutral foundations, system fonts, responsive layouts with mobile sidebar drawer.

<artifact identifier="splitflow-prototype" type="text/html" title="SplitFlow — Expense Splitting App">
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>SplitFlow — Expense Splitting App</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: oklch(97.5% 0.004 240);
      --surface: oklch(100% 0 0);
      --fg: oklch(18% 0.02 240);
      --fg-secondary: oklch(40% 0.018 240);
      --muted: oklch(55% 0.015 240);
      --border: oklch(91% 0.006 240);
      --border-strong: oklch(84% 0.01 240);
      --accent: oklch(56% 0.14 168);
      --accent-light: oklch(92% 0.04 168);
      --accent-hover: oklch(50% 0.14 168);
      --positive: oklch(52% 0.13 155);
      --positive-bg: oklch(95% 0.03 155);
      --negative: oklch(55% 0.16 25);
      --negative-bg: oklch(95% 0.03 25);
      --radius-sm: 8px;
      --radius-md: 12px;
      --radius-lg: 16px;
      --radius-xl: 24px;
      --radius-full: 999px;
      --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px oklch(0% 0 0 / 0.04);
      --shadow-md: 0 4px 12px oklch(0% 0 0 / 0.06);
      --shadow-lg: 0 8px 30px oklch(0% 0 0 / 0.08);
      --font-display: 'Söhne', 'Avenir Next', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;
      --font-body: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Text', system-ui, sans-serif;
      --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
      --transition: 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--fg);
      background: var(--bg);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    body {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100dvh;
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }
    a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; transition: color var(--transition); }
    a:hover { color: var(--accent-hover); }
    .launcher { max-width: 720px; width: 100%; }
    .launcher-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .launcher-logo { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .launcher-logo-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      background: var(--accent);
      display: grid; place-items: center;
    }
    .launcher-logo-icon svg { width: 28px; height: 28px; color: white; }
    .launcher-logo-text {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--fg);
    }
    .launcher-subtitle {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: var(--fg-secondary);
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .screen-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .screen-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--fg);
      transition: all var(--transition);
    }
    .screen-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      color: var(--fg);
    }
    .screen-card-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      background: var(--accent-light);
      display: grid; place-items: center;
    }
    .screen-card-icon svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; color: var(--accent); }
    .screen-card-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; }
    .screen-card-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.4; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="launcher">
    <div class="launcher-header">
      <div class="launcher-logo">
        <div class="launcher-logo-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="launcher-logo-text">SplitFlow</span>
